      "description": "At the end of your Movement phase, you can select one friendly <span class=\"tooltip00378\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00378\" data-tooltip-anchor=\"#tooltip_content00378\"><span class=\"kwb\">ORKS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">VEHICLE</span></span> model within 3\" of this model. That <span class=\"kwb\">VEHICLE</span> model regains up to D3 lost wounds, and, until the start of your next Movement phase, each time that <span class=\"kwb\">VEHICLE</span> model makes an attack, add 1 to the Hit roll. Each model can only be selected for this ability once per turn.",
